data.description: Beautiful Texas Style Hill Country two story home on oversized lot, 5 bedrooms, 4 baths, study/office, side entry garage. Almost 4,000 Sq ft open floor plan home that shows like a MODEL with all of the designer touches. Any chef would die for this kitchen!!! There is a gas cooktop, double oven, beautiful island island, walk-in pantry, tons of cabinets & counter space, designer backslash, amazing countertops and built-in stainless steel appliances. The open floor plan is ideal for entertaining. The spacious owner's suite is split and offers a walk-in shower and a garden tub. HUGE walk-in closet. Secondary bedroom located downstairs. Three bedroom upstairs including jack & Jill. Utility room includes custom cabinets. Owners have made numerous upgrades that must be seen to appreciate.  River Chase subdivision just minutes from downtown New Braunfels and Gruene.
